<bibRefCitation author="Robertson and Allen" box="[872,1178,1663,1689]" firstAuthor="Robertson" pageId="222" pageNumber="223" refId="ref316713" refString="Robertson, D. R. &amp; Allen, G. R. (2002) Shorefishes of the tropical eastern Pacific: an information system. CD-ROM. Smithsonian Tropical Research Institute, Balboa, Panama." type="book" year="2002">Robertson and Allen 2002</bibRefCitation>
